      <me>
        A = \begin{bmatrix}
        -7 \amp 8 \\ -6 \amp 7
        \end{bmatrix}
      </me>. <!-- 1, -1 -->
      Find the characteristic polynomial and the eigenvalues of <m>A</m>. 
    </p>
  </statement>
</exercise>
<exercise>
