        A = \begin{bmatrix}
        7 \amp -3 \\ 6 \amp -2
        \end{bmatrix}
      </me>. <!-- 1, 4 -->
      Find the characteristic polynomial and the eigenvalues of <m>A</m>. 
    </p>
  </statement>
</exercise>
